Country Club Course and Courts
Not the typical resort or development course, Magnolia Point was designed for GOLF and TENNIS.  The magnificent oaks, magnolia trees, and tall pines are the backdrop for your final approach shots.
Golfers and tennis players can take advantage of the beautiful Jacksonville scenery, executive amenities open to the public, and first-class facilities.
Magnolia Point is the most beautiful Jacksonville golf and country club, with no parallel fairways. Golfers will enjoy a tranquil and scenic view of the 1000-acre community that is abundant with wildlife.

Weddings & Banquets
Couples choose Magnolia Point to host their wedding rehearsal, ceremony, reception and showers because we not only offer the most elegant banquet rooms, but our onsite catering and event planning makes every event that much more special.
Our banquet rooms are equipped to host events of all sizes and our outdoor and indoor venue spaces are perfect for every event.

Our Wedding Venue
Magnolia Point Golf and Country Club is a country club wedding venue located in Green Cove Springs, Florida.
Located only minutes from Orange Park and Jacksonville, this beautiful event venue offers scenic views of their famous golf course along with both outdoor and indoor event spaces for couples to create the ceremony and reception they’ve always envisioned on their beautiful grounds.
Facilities and Capacity
Magnolia Point Golf and Country Club is a spacious wedding and event venue with various event spaces for wedding ceremonies, receptions, anniversary parties, and more. Their event spaces accommodate up to 135 guests and comfortably host small and intimate events and large and extravagant celebrations. The venue offers three event spaces to choose from, both indoor and outdoor. Clients can enjoy an unforgettable wedding ceremony underneath a pergola draped in chiffon, located in their breathtaking gardens, with lush foliage and relaxing fountains and waterfalls. This venue offers the perfect natural setting for your wedding photos, and clients can take advantage of the venue’s beautifully manicured grounds to set a beautiful backdrop for your images. Clients can also enjoy using Magnolia’s Crystal dining room, where less is more. Couples can enjoy making memories of the picturesque views, inviting atmosphere, and charming getaway at this semi-private country club. If you’d like a more casual setting, The Pub is a great alternative ~ a modern gastro-pub feel with copper top bars, exposed brick pillars edged out with metal and raw concrete floors, your modern event awaits.

Services Offered
Magnolia Point Golf and Country Club is a full-service wedding and event venue.
The staff offers custom wedding packages for clients to choose the services that align with their wedding vision.
They will ensure that each detail of your wedding day is to your liking, with event items for outdoor ceremonies such as chairs, tables, a pergola, and a paver walkway with a stage.
In addition, an on-site wedding coordinator will work with you to select the details of your wedding celebration, such as menu choices, bar services, and other wedding details.
Other event services include:

Cuisine

Our from-scratch-kitchen ran by our Executive Chef, and culinary team, created these menus with your guests in mind.
These menus will delight any palate!

Planning Your Next Event
Truly Unforgettable… Our professional staff will bring elegance and exceptional service to help make your wedding ceremony, reception, rehearsal dinner, corporate event, celebration of life, family reunion, anniversary, birthday, banquet, or other special occasion become a lasting memory.
From the scenic views of our famous golf course setting, to the beauty of our outdoor venue and spacious indoor banquet facility, we cater to your event with the utmost care and planning.
Our experienced, friendly specialists have thought out every detail, assuring your event will not only satisfy your requirements, but will exceed your expectations.
The secluded setting of Magnolia Point makes it an exceptional location to celebrate this very cherished and special time in your life. Located only minutes from Orange Park and Jacksonville,
Magnolia Point is the perfect setting for your special day.
Call us today for a tour of our beautiful property at 904.269.9276 ext. 4.
We would love to help you plan your upcoming event!

About Our Club
Magnolia Point Golf and Country Club is located off U.S. Highway 17 south of Jacksonville in Green Cove Springs. Not the typical resort or development course, Magnolia Point was designed for GOLF and TENNIS. Magnolia Point is home to 18 holes of fantastic golf. Our golf course, located in Green Cove Springs is one of the best in Jacksonville and North Florida.
The magnificent oaks, magnolia trees and tall pines are the backdrop for your final approach shots—not someone’s swimming pool or bedroom window.
With no parallel fairways, golfers will enjoy a tranquil and scenic view of the 1000-acre community that is abundant with wildlife including wild turkeys, deer, hawks, alligators, waterfowl, snakes, turtles and an occasional bald eagle. It offers outstanding conditions, scenic views with abundant local wildlife.
The United States Golf Association (USGA) selected Magnolia Point Golf and Country Club as the August 2006 final sectional qualifying location for the U.S. Amateur.
Our practice facility has a partial synthetic turf tee line driving range along with grass for you to improve your game in multiple ways, a full-sized putting green with multiple pin placements for practicing, and a full-size chipping area.
We proudly host our Men’s Golf Association along with our Ladies 18-Hole + 9-Hole Golf Leagues. We are also the host of Clay High School’s Boys & Girls Golf Teams.

We proudly host our Men’s Golf Association along with our Ladies 18-Hole + 9-Hole Golf Leagues. We are also the host of Clay High School’s Boys & Girls Golf Teams.
Magnolia Point is also a premier wedding venue location in Green Cove Springs and the Jacksonville area. We are proud to have the most beautiful outdoor wedding venue in the area. Captivated by nature and beauty, you’ll feel you’ve escaped into a tropical paradise.
Our Crystal Dining Room is pure elegance. You can dress it up or down and it is just perfect. Offering complete wedding services with several package options along with many years of experience in events, our staff is waiting to help create your majestic moments.
We also specialize in weddings, rehearsal dinners, birthdays parties, anniversary celebrations, bridal and baby showers, celebrations of life, corporate dinners, holiday parties along with club groups and club events.
The Pub at MP offers excellent food and beverage in the clubhouse restaurant Our menu offers a wide range of delicious items that has something for everyone.
Our clubhouse dining is run by our executive chef along with his culinary team that is sure to delight your palate.
We change our menu seasonally and run a “from scratch kitchen”. From our dressings to our entrees, you can be sure everything is fresh.

Magnolia Point Tennis has 7 Har-Tru clay tennis courts, 4 are lit for night play.
The tennis program offers excellent instruction and is active in many local tennis leagues. We also offer competitive teams for ladies, mixed doubles and men’s league.
We are also the host of Clay High School’s Boys & Girls Tennis Teams. Our newly renovated Activity Zone boosts sand volleyball, one Pickleball court and a playground for tiny tots.
This is all located next to our Junior Olympic sized swimming pool, open dawn to dusk daily – weather permitting.
